title: [FSX] PMDG 747LCF
description:
Here's the PMDG 747LCF for all your flying pleasure! 


How to Install:

1. Run the installer

2.Open 'Enable Button' only once you reach the validation page and then don't click         'Next' but click the 'Back' button. The installer automatically skips the vallidation page! :)

3. Continue with the installation.

4. Enjoy flying! :D

Note: 1. PMDG 747-400X is required to be installed prior to installing the 747LCF.
      2. Once 747LCF is installed select 747LCF mode in the PMDG 747-8&400 Config     Manager before flying.
